headline: Agilent to Announce Second-Quarter Fiscal Year 2025 Financial Results on May 28
summary: SANTA CLARA, Calif., April 16, 2025--Agilent Technologies Inc. (NYSE: A) will release financial results for the second quarter of fiscal year 2025 after the stock market closes on Wednesday, May 28. In addition, the company will host a conference call to discuss the results at 1:30 p.m. PDT on the same day.
